# MerrySails — environment variable reference (placeholders only).
# Copy what you need into a gitignored .env / .env.local. NEVER put real
# secrets in this file — it is committed to the repo.

# ── Partner Brands (sister-brand Neon DBs) ──────────────────────────────
# Read-only cross-DB connection strings for the "Partner Brands" admin tab
# (/admin/partner-brands), which shows Luma Yacht + Vesper reservations from
# their OWN, SEPARATE databases. Storage stays separate per brand — MerrySails
# only reads + lightly manages status. If these are unset, the tab renders a
# graceful "configure partner DB URLs" state and MerrySails still builds/runs.
# Set the real values in the Vercel project env (or a local gitignored env file).
LUMA_DATABASE_URL="postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST.neon.tech/neondb?sslmode=require"
VESPER_DATABASE_URL="postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST.neon.tech/neondb?sslmode=require"
